Hainan Airlines Company Profile  Hainan Airlines Holding Co., Ltd. (hereafter referred to as "Hainan Airlines") was established in January, 1993 in Hainan Province, China's largest special economic zone and free trade port. Hainan Airlines is committed to providing passengers with comprehensive and seamless airline services and creating a safe and comfortable travel experience.  As of 2023, Hainan Airlines and its subsidiaries operated nearly 1,800 domestic and international routes, including nearly 1,600 domestic routes, covering all provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the central government in the Chinese mainland, as well as 100 international and regional routes to 37 overseas cities, including scheduled passenger flights, passenger charter flights, and passenger-to-cargo flights, covering Asia, Europe, Africa, North America and Oceania regions. Hainan Airlines has also actively responded to The Belt and Road Initiative by focusing on building a world-class airline network. Hainan Airlines and its subsidiaries have established operational bases and branches in 24 cities including Haikou,Beijing,Guangzhou and Shenzhen.  From 1993 until now, Hainan Airlines has been operating safely for 31 years and maintains an excellent operational record. In February 2024, Hainan Airlines was awarded the “One Star Flight Safety Diamond Award” by the Civil Aviation Administration of China for achieving 10 million consecutive hours of safe flight which is a great achievement.  Hainan Airlines is the first and only SKYTRAX 5-Star airline in the Chinese Mainland, who has been awarded the SKYTRAX 5-Star Airline for 13 consecutive years since 2011. This honor is Hainan Airlines highest level of recognition for our outstanding service, and also represents praise from the passengers for our high quality services.  Fly Your Dreams—Hainan Airlines.

Neat Reader is an App specifically designed for reading EPUB e-books. It is trusted and loved by millions of people around the world.  Neat Reader is a cross-platform ePub reader that supports "cloud storage, multi-end synchronization" and supports all the mainstream OS. You can open and read ePub files on any platform and experience a seamless reading experience.  Neat Reader can perfectly parse various ePub files and provide a variety of reading features such as notes, search, customization and more. Effectively meet the user's personalized needs for reading ePub.  IMPORT & VIEW EPUB FILES · Easily import your ePub files by wifi-transfer and other convenient methods. · Choose Neat Reader while you are opening EPUB files in other apps, the file will be automatically added to Neat Reader library. · Quickly open and view EPUB books. · Use a variety of ways to navigate within the EPUB book.  ANNOTATE EPUB BOOKS · Highlight book contents and write notes on them. · Quickly jump to the highlight position inside the EPUB books. · Highlight color changes automatically when you change the theme.  CUSTOMIZATION · Change the font size, style of the EPUB books. · Select the most suitable color theme for the environment.  IN-APP PURCHASE If you need to read your EPUB books on more than two devices, no matter what device they are and what system they are running, you should upgrade your account to Premium. Neat Reader Premium will give you 10GB cloud storage and when your EPUB book is uploaded to the cloud, all the reading data will be synchronized automatically. Put it simply, when you are Premium, your EPUB books will be stored in the cloud and you can get seamless reading experience on all your devices.  MANAGE EPUB FILES · You can create a category for your books and manage them in your way. · With 10 GB cloud storage, you can upload about 5000 EPUB files to the cloud storage. KISS: Read & Write Romance is the premiere app for the best serialized fiction in the world!   Our stories feature high-stakes drama and heart-stopping romances. From billionaires to bad boys, werewolves to sports stars, Kiss features the kinds of stories that will sweep you away. Our authors are New York Times and USA Today Bestselling authors, Indie and TikTok superstars and the best emerging authors from across the globe.   Come discover your next new obsession—we have thousands of books and authors to choose from. Download and start reading for free now!  Kiss features stories of all genres along with heat levels to match however naughty or nice you’re feeling. So indulge your fantasies. And be sure to check out some of our fan-favorite stories:  Forbidden Temptation: My Mafia Fiance's Alpha Father “Chamomile, lavender,” he murmurs, closing his eyes, taking in my scent.  “So fresh and clean…untainted by the scent of another wolf.” Then he opens his eyes and stares into my bewildered face, wanting to see my reaction as he says, “You must be a virgin.” My lip trembles.  His eyes eat me up, savoring the quiver of my lips, my wide, terrified eyes. I swear I feel his tongue flick over my pulse point, hear his low groan. “So innocent, so pure…” His grip tightens, and even confined by silver that should keep it from happening, his wolf flashes in his eyes. “Two of my favorite things to destroy.”  Snatched a Billionaire to be My Husband Her scumbag fiancé ended their engagement after her family went bankrupt. Seeking solace, she went to a bar and ended up sleeping with the wealthiest man in the country, coincidentally, also that scumbag's uncle. Initially, he insisted it was a mistake and had no intention of maintaining any further connection with her. However, he couldn't resist lending a hand whenever she needed financial assistance or when she faced humiliation from that scumbag and his new girlfriend. Then she tricked him into marriage by faking a pregnancy, to seek revenge against her ex, and surprisingly, find happiness in their marriage. Yet, she constantly lived in fear of her secret being exposed.  Mated to the Alpha and His Beta I’ve been dreading my eighteenth birthday for as long as I can remember. My mating day was even worse than I could have imagined. Not only was I mated to the Alpha and the Beta, they don’t want me, and everyone in the pack knows it.  Instead, they want another girl. And they’ll do whatever it takes to have her.  Kidnapped By My Fated Mate Bella Malum leads a perfectly normal life given her upbringing. But after being convinced to submit a DNA test to determine where her long-lost parents came from, her entire world shifts. Somehow, she’s a powerful psi who was promised to a Domini prince...as his mate. Dominic—AKA Nic—Regnum is the century old leader who has waited years to meet, and claim Bella. And he is less than thrilled when she refuses to come quietly. But Nic holds information back from her—information that changes everything she thought she knew about her past, present, and future. Learn a new language with the most fun educational app in the world! HelloWords, 120% visual learning! Only 3 minutes a day!  How can I get rid of boring lessons and become more interested when learning a new language? HelloWords has a game-changing approach to language learning! We take the bore out of vocabulary learning! The barriers that keep you from starting to learn languages are finally outdated.  With over 29 free languages to choose from, HelloWords’ quick and interactive word games make learning a new language fun.  Here are the key features that make HelloWords right for you:  【29 languages available】 We offer the following languages that you want to learn for FREE! Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Cantonese, American English, British English, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Russian, European Spanish, Latin American Spanish, Brazilian Portuguese, European Portuguese, Arabic, Vietnamese, Turkish, Thai, Norwegian, Polish, Dutch, Swedish, Hindi, Indonesian, Hungarian, Danish, Icelandic, Hebrew  With HelloWords, you'll be able to master language learning with more ease and have real-life conversations with more confidence. Whether you need a Spanish learning app, Japanese learning app, or whether you want to learn Korean or learn French in depth, or improve your German, HelloWords is the choice.  【SRS  memorization method】 In order to never forget vocabulary again, HelloWords uses "spaced repetition system (SRS)" based on the Ebbinghaus forgetting curve. This shows that calculated intervals of repetition allow you to memorize words more effectively.  HelloWords wants to turn you into a language learning addict.  【Game-based vocabulary learning】 Why do people get hooked on playing games? Not only because they're fun but also because you can get feedback on everything you do, and they help you set goals. Now we have integrated these aspects into HelloWords. Notice: With the correct game-based vocabulary learning approach, you accumulate considerable knowledge of a new language instead of wasting time!  【Advanced learning statistics】 After each session you’ll see your daily progress with a detailed report of all the words that you studied, including the words that you've already mastered by clicking "Senior filter".   As the amount of vocabulary you grasp increases, your language level will improve automatically. Visible signs of progress make you more confident.  HelloWords makes language learning effortless fun.   【Strategically selected vocabulary】 The foreign language team of HelloTalk handpicked 3000+ practical words from 168 topics that cover 90% of everyday word usage. These are words you’ll actually use when you travel to a country where the language is spoken.  【Fragmented learning: only 3 minutes a day】 HelloWords limits your learning time to 3 minutes. This might sound crazy, but it works like a charm. The time limit encourages intense focus which further enhances the effectiveness of memorization.  Whether you're learning languages for travel abroad, school, career development, family and friends, or just simply enjoy learning languages, you'll love studying with HelloWords.  Learn words in just 3 minutes and easily fit language learning into your busy schedule.  No excuses: you can ALWAYS find 3 minutes!  Have any questions? Our original intention is to create such an Android note-taking software:  It reads and writes file directories in a multi-level format, so that we can synchronize our note files between computers and mobile phones through cloud synchronization. As long as there is an Internet connection, we can turn on our mobile phones and record our thoughts at any time and anywhere.  Our data is only stored on the device and our own cloud disk, so our notes will be more secure.  It supports Markdown basic syntax, can render MathJax mathematical formulas, and provides a variety of themes and syntax highlighting.  It can help us insert pictures and reference other notes in the form of relative paths. In this way, we can use pictures as we like in our notes without any picture bed.  It can provide us with many ways to manage our notes. In addition to multi-level directories, you can also break directory restrictions and categorize your own notes in the form of tags.  It can provide an efficient search mechanism and can find the keywords we want in all notes.  Pictures are notes. We hope to be able to quickly record what is happening and our thoughts in the form of pictures + notes.  In order to organize pictures, it should also provide functions such as picture cropping, transformation and processing.  We want it to save what we write in real time...  We want it to be able to export notes to HTML, text, PDF and images...  We hope that it can make full use of platform features and provide some personalized functions, such as desktop widgets, shortcuts, notification bar buttons...  We also hope...  So, we made Leaf Note.  Leaf Note is a private and secure note-taking software that supports Markdown syntax and cloud synchronization. It is not only powerful and smooth, but also has an elegant appearance.  If a worker wants to do his job well, he must first sharpen his tools. We hope it helps you better record your thoughts.  You can try it now.  No matter you have any comments or suggestions, you can give us feedback at any time.  Thanks!

I have a Casio G-Series radio watch, but it is always unable to receive radio waves from time signal station, so I started to write an application to solve this problem.  After some research, I finally wrote this application, which can perfectly simulate the timing signal and happily calibrate the time.  Usage method: 1. Adjust the volume of phone to the maximum. 2. Switch the radio controlled watch / clock to manual wave receiving mode. 3. Click the "start" button. 4. Place the watch / clock near the phone speakers. 5. The synchronization process generally takes 3-10 minutes, please wait patiently.  Matters needing attention: 1. Please try to use the software in a quiet environment to avoid signal interference. 2. The volume of the mobile phone must be adjusted to the maximum. It's too small and the effect is not good.  Characteristic: 1. Supports simulation of all types of Time Wave Signal: * China BPC * USA WWVB * Japan JJY40 / JJY60 * Germany DCF77 * British MSF 2. The unique "Beast Mode" provides higher frequency simulation signals and faster sync.  Contact information: Please contact me if you have any use questions *QQ: 3364918353 *Email: 3364918353@qq.com
Supports local, LAN (smb v2/v3), and webdav.

One App, Four Systems! EMBER Smart Heating Control has been updated to control a new range of EPH Controls products with the EMBER logo including the smart Radiator System RS and smart Underfloor System US.  Ask your installer for EPH EMBER today.  With improved and intuitive navigation you will have easier access to your homes heating system and improved control of multiple zones and multiple homes from the palm of your hand.  EMBER Smart Heating can control 4 types of heating systems:  EMBER PS – Programmer System. Version 1: This system is comprised of our wireless enabled R-Series programmers, thermostats using the GW01 gateway Version 2: This system is comprised of our wireless enabled R-Series version 2 programmers and thermostats using the GW04 gateway. EMBER RS – Radiator System. This system is comprised of our new RF16 controller, eTRV and eTRV-HW using the GW04 gateway. EMBER TS – Thermostat System. Version 1: This system is comprised of our WiFi ready CP4-OT and CP4-HW-OT thermostats using the GW03 gateway. Version 2: This system is comprised of our version 2 WiFi ready CP4v2, CP4D and CP4-HW thermostats using the GW04 gateway  EMBER US –Underfloor System. This system is comprised of our new Underfloor heating controller UFH10-RF and thermostats using the GW04 gateway. New Features Grouping It is now possible to group zones to allow control of multiple areas at once, the user can set up to 10 groups and add their zones to these groups for easier control of the whole house. Setback (PS and US only) It is possible to set a heating zone to operate in a setback mode. This will allow the user to set a value from 1-10°C. When the system is timed off it will turn the temperature down by this value and activate if it falls below the lower level.  Quick Boost It is now possible to set the Quick Boost temperature for heating zones with an expanded range. Eco Monitor The Eco monitor is now available on the TS and all version 2 products in the EMBER range. It can be activated in the Home Info section of the menu. It will show temperature logs for each zone and overall usage of the system in hours.   Advance Function (PS and US only) Advance function can now be activated from the Zone Control screen.  Improved Setup process For enhanced security and convenience, this version allows the installer to set up a customer home with their own credentials. When the home owner logs in, the installer will be removed from the home and the home owner will be assigned Super Admin status.  Upgraded User Management The user management function has been improved with an extra security layer and more detailed user information.  Schedule Overview A complete overview of your programming schedule is now available on the Schedule screen.

WarmLink makes it possible for you communicate with your heat pump easily from a local WiFi network(IEEE 802.11b/g/n standard WiFi network), or remotely over the Internet. WarmLink is compatible with heat pump that must be with WiFi or DTU module that provided by the product suppliers.  With WarmLink, you can: - be able to monitor the state of the heat pump, such as the available water flow volume, the current water temperature, the current running mode, etc. - be able to set the state of the heat pump, such as ON/OFF setting, target water temperature setting, mode setting, timer setting, etc. - be able to get more information about the water temperature changes through temperature curve. - be informed of any failures of the heat pump. - be provided with considerate service that the suppliers will solve any detected problems of the units in the background before you ask for assistance.  To confirm whether this app can communicate with the controller of your heat pump, please check it with your supplier.

What is VPN  A virtual private network (VPN) extends a private network across a public network, and enables users to send and receive data across shared or public networks as if their computing devices were directly connected to the private network. Applications running across the VPN may therefore benefit from the functionality, security, and management of the private network.  Individual Internet users may secure their transactions with a VPN, to circumvent geo-restrictions and censorship, or to connect to proxy servers for the purpose of protecting personal identity and location. However, some Internet sites block access to known VPN technology to prevent the circumvention of their geo-restrictions.  VPNs cannot make online connections completely anonymous, but they can usually increase privacy and security. To prevent disclosure of private information, VPNs typically allow only authenticated remote access using tunneling protocols and encryption techniques.  Mobile virtual private networks are used in settings where an endpoint of the VPN is not fixed to a single IP address.

What is VPN  A virtual private network (VPN) extends a private network across a public network, and enables users to send and receive data across shared or public networks as if their computing devices were directly connected to the private network. Applications running across the VPN may therefore benefit from the functionality, security, and management of the private network.  Individual Internet users may secure their transactions with a VPN, to circumvent geo-restrictions and censorship, or to connect to proxy servers for the purpose of protecting personal identity and location. However, some Internet sites block access to known VPN technology to prevent the circumvention of their geo-restrictions.  VPNs cannot make online connections completely anonymous, but they can usually increase privacy and security. To prevent disclosure of private information, VPNs typically allow only authenticated remote access using tunneling protocols and encryption techniques.  Mobile virtual private networks are used in settings where an endpoint of the VPN is not fixed to a single IP address.

Hello folks! Welcome to Tech-Freedom for Visually Impaired. There is no doubt that over the last few years various apps were developed for the visually challenged to tackle various issues like screen reader, word processers, pdf readers and so on. In this scenario, we (V.I. Developers) are here with the multi-feature android app “Tech-Freedom”. Tech-Freedom is a multi-feature android app. It is ads free and cost-free app. It is stable from android 5 to 13. It has following features: 1.	App Backup. 2.	Audio Editor 3.	Cash Reader. 4.	Document Converter. 5.	Document Saver. 6.	Image Reader. 7.	Instant Reader. 8.	Link Saver. 9.	My Player. 10.	Notepad. 11.	Password Saver. 12.	PDF Reader. 13.	Text Translator. 14.	Video Editor 15.	Voice Recorder. These features are developed with having accessibility into the mind. Also, Accessibility is evaluated with Google’s accessibility suite (Talkback) during development. *App Backup: By using this feature, you’ll be able to take and share backup of your installed apps. Backed up apps will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/App Backups. *Audio Editor: Audio Editor is one of the most demanding features of our app. It’ll allow you to cut and merge audios. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Cash Reader: Blind people are often stuck while detecting currencies. To solve that problem, we design our own AI neural network to detect currencies using phone’s camera. Currently we’re only supporting Indian bank notes: 10 Rupee. 20 Rupee. 50 Rupee. 100 Rupee. 200 Rupee. 500 Rupee. 2000 Rupee. *Document Converter: This feature helps you to convert PDF, office and TXT files with each other. The converted files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Document Saver: By using Document Saver, you’ll be able to create TXT and PDF files from your text very easily. The saved files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Image Reader: By using Tech-Freedom, your images will speak to you Directly. We have both online and offline image reader. Online image reader is most advance and accurate image processer. Whereas offline image reader is designed to be worked offline. *Instant Reader: An Instant Reader is used to instantly read out the text in front of camera. *Link Saver: By using our Link Saver, you’ll have all your important links saved. *My Player: My Player is used to play audios and videos on your device. *Notepad: By using our online notepad, you’ll be able to save your notes online. *Password Saver: By using our Password Saver, you’ll be able to save your account’s passwords offline. *PDF Reader: Reading PDF is more challenging task for a visually impaired. But it’ll be very easy to read it now with our most accurate and fast PDF Reader. It has many features to perform on your PDFs. Also, you can copy, translate, save, export and share content of your PDFs very easily. Ability to set bookmark is added too. You can also open your password protected PDFs very easily. In today’s world, PDF is not creating with just text, but it’s composed of scanned documents and images. With our advance and most accurate OCR engine, your PDFs can be rendered very well. *Text Translator: Text Translator is used to translate your text within 135 languages. *Video Editor: An accessible video editor is the dream of visually impaired. It includes: Video Cutter. Video Merger. Video to Audio. Image to Video. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Voice Recorder: By using Voice Recorder, you can record your audios. Official website of Tech-Freedom: https://techfreedom.in For any queries / suggestion, email us: info@techfreedom.in Best regards! V.I. Developers.

Primele referiri la proprietatile vindecatoare ale plantelor medicinale dateaza de acum 6.000 de ani, cand vracii vremii obtineau din plante extracte sub forma de tincturi, uleiuri, creme, ceaiuri, prafuri etc. Ei au pus atunci bazele unor tratamente care s-au pastrat pana in zilele noastre si care s-au dovedit foarte eficiente In general, s-a descoperit ca tratamentul cu plante medicinale da rezultate foarte bune in afectiunile usoare si in stadiile incipiente ale bolilor. In bolile cronice, acest tratament are un rol adjuvant si poate contribui la o reversibilitate a simptomelor sau leziunilor. Anumite ceaiuri conduc la inlaturarea rapida a unor simptome, dar tratamentele naturale complexe actioneaza in timp. Vindecarea  este un proces de durata, in functie de vechimea bolii, cauzele ei etc. Exista numerosi practicieni ai medicinei naturale care au demonstrat, prin studii efectuate in clinici, ca inclusiv bolile grave pot fi vindecate. Cele mai cunoscute si usor aplicabile metode de extragere si de folosire a substantelor active din plante medicinale sunt infuzia, decoctul, maceratul, sucul natural, cataplasma, tinctura, vinul medicinal, otetul aromatic, uleiurile medicinale, inhalatia, gargara. Vei descoperi cum problemele de sanatate au o solutie simpla si fara niciun fel de efecte secundare! ________________________________________________________________________________________  The first references to the healing properties of medicinal plants dating back 6,000 years, when healers weather made from plants extracts as tinctures, oils, creams, teas, powders etc. They then put the foundations of treatments that have been preserved until today and that proved very effective In general, it was found that treatment with herbs give good results in mild disease in the early stages of disease. In chronic diseases, this treatment has a role adjuvant and can contribute to reversibility of symptoms or injuries. Some teas lead to rapid elimination of symptoms, but complex acts while natural treatments. Healing is a long process, depending on the duration of the disease, its causes etc. There are many natural medicine practitioners who have demonstrated by studies conducted in clinics, including serious diseases that can be cured. The best known and easily applicable method for extracting and using active ingredients are herbal infusion, decoction, macerate, natural juice, poultice, tincture, medicinal wine, vinegar aromatic, medicinal oils, inhalers, gargle. You'll discover how health problems have a simple solution without any side effects!

Safety Watch is a product designed for children and parents. The app can be connected with the watch by wearing the watch on the children’s wrist and its supporting app on the parents’ mobile phone. Parents can make mutual calls between the watch and the mobile phone, accurately locate the children’s position, and send voice message between the app and the watch by setting watch-related functions in the app. Main Functional Features: 1.Phone Function: The phone module is installed in the hardware of the watch to allow calls between the phone and the watch, and between watches, thereby making communication and connection between parents and children more convenient.  2.Location Function: A GPS chip and WiFi module are installed in the hardware of the watch, enabling the APP to show the precise position of the watch whether outdoors or indoors. 3.Chat Function: Voice messages can be sent between the watch and the APP, realizing a new form of communication between children and parents.  4.Step Counting Function: The child’s number of steps can be viewed on the watch in order to help the parents record the child’s progress step by step and ensure their healthy growth. 5.Class Mode: Parents can set the times of the child’s classes. When the child attends school wearing the watch, they will not be distracted from learning by playing with the watch. 6.Contacts: Parents can use the APP to manage the contacts on their child’s watch, thereby making sure that their child will not be harassed by unknown calls while also preventing their child from making random calls.

This game is tailor made for kids. Kids have to spot out 5 differences between two photos. All pictures all hd pictures and interested by kids. They are all from happy box games. Come and try! It free and fun.  Playing this game, children can quickly and accurately find the differences, and they can effectively enhance the powers of observation and attention. With better learning ability and observation skills, children can be easier to access to the learning state in schools and easier to learn form the teachers.  Spot the difference puzzles are sometimes known as spot the difference game. The goal is to find a number of differences between two images, which may be drawings, computer graphics, or photographs. The game offers you a massive selection of puzzles and games at all levels of difficulty for everyone.   Two types of game mode:   Checkpoints mode - Player can play the game on a stage basis. Players are provided either 3 hints for use during the course of one game. The number of remaining hints is indicated by the number of magnifying glass images centered at the top of bottom of the screen. Players touch one of these icons to reveal one of the remaining differences. Differences located by hints are immediately counted as found and are surrounded by a red circle.  Challenge mode - Player can play the game with all factors in random basis. Players are provided either 3 hints for use during the course of one game and try to complete as many level as possible. Pictures are provided in random basis.

Hello folks! Welcome to Tech-Freedom for Visually Impaired. There is no doubt that over the last few years various apps were developed for the visually challenged to tackle various issues like screen reader, word processers, pdf readers and so on. In this scenario, we (V.I. Developers) are here with the multi-feature android app “Tech-Freedom”. Tech-Freedom is a multi-feature android app. It is ads free and cost-free app. It is stable from android 5 to 13. It has following features: 1.	App Backup. 2.	Audio Editor 3.	Cash Reader. 4.	Document Converter. 5.	Document Saver. 6.	Image Reader. 7.	Instant Reader. 8.	Link Saver. 9.	My Player. 10.	Notepad. 11.	Password Saver. 12.	PDF Reader. 13.	Text Translator. 14.	Video Editor 15.	Voice Recorder. These features are developed with having accessibility into the mind. Also, Accessibility is evaluated with Google’s accessibility suite (Talkback) during development. *App Backup: By using this feature, you’ll be able to take and share backup of your installed apps. Backed up apps will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/App Backups. *Audio Editor: Audio Editor is one of the most demanding features of our app. It’ll allow you to cut and merge audios. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Cash Reader: Blind people are often stuck while detecting currencies. To solve that problem, we design our own AI neural network to detect currencies using phone’s camera. Currently we’re only supporting Indian bank notes: 10 Rupee. 20 Rupee. 50 Rupee. 100 Rupee. 200 Rupee. 500 Rupee. 2000 Rupee. *Document Converter: This feature helps you to convert PDF, office and TXT files with each other. The converted files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Document Saver: By using Document Saver, you’ll be able to create TXT and PDF files from your text very easily. The saved files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Image Reader: By using Tech-Freedom, your images will speak to you Directly. We have both online and offline image reader. Online image reader is most advance and accurate image processer. Whereas offline image reader is designed to be worked offline. *Instant Reader: An Instant Reader is used to instantly read out the text in front of camera. *Link Saver: By using our Link Saver, you’ll have all your important links saved. *My Player: My Player is used to play audios and videos on your device. *Notepad: By using our online notepad, you’ll be able to save your notes online. *Password Saver: By using our Password Saver, you’ll be able to save your account’s passwords offline. *PDF Reader: Reading PDF is more challenging task for a visually impaired. But it’ll be very easy to read it now with our most accurate and fast PDF Reader. It has many features to perform on your PDFs. Also, you can copy, translate, save, export and share content of your PDFs very easily. Ability to set bookmark is added too. You can also open your password protected PDFs very easily. In today’s world, PDF is not creating with just text, but it’s composed of scanned documents and images. With our advance and most accurate OCR engine, your PDFs can be rendered very well. *Text Translator: Text Translator is used to translate your text within 135 languages. *Video Editor: An accessible video editor is the dream of visually impaired. It includes: Video Cutter. Video Merger. Video to Audio. Image to Video. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Voice Recorder: By using Voice Recorder, you can record your audios. Official website of Tech-Freedom: https://techfreedom.in For any queries / suggestion, email us: info@techfreedom.in Best regards! V.I. Developers.

The Convention of Baptist Churches Independent in Bahia (CIBIBA) is a Regional Convention, affiliated to the Convention of Baptist Churches Independent (CIBI).  Independent Baptists in Brazil originate from Örebro, Sweden Mission. Founded in 1892 by john ongman.  In 1911 a member of the Swedish colony installed in Vila Guarani, (today Guarani Missions) in Rio Grande do Sul, writes a letter requesting a missionary. This moves the heart of john ongman, president of the mission, and then sent missionary Erik Jansson, who arrives in Porto Alegre on 15 June 1912 and remains there for some time. On 12 September of that same year he arrives at Vila Guarani, being greeted by a large number of Swedish immigrants.  Not far from the Guarani village are German immigrants coming from Europe. Among them a group of converted brothers, who need care. Upon learning of the arrival of a Swedish missionary seek and are met. Erik Jansson goes to visit German immigrants, baptize converts each month, organized churches and congregations, which bind the Evangelical Baptist Convention of South Rio Grande founded in 1919. In 1939 the first churches start performing their annual Assemblies in the language that bring overseas: German. In 1958 the Independent Baptist work reaches the state of Paraná, spreads and several churches are organized.  In 1952, the city of Ijuí-RS, is founded the Convention of the Evangelical Baptist Churches Independent in Brazil, with the objective of expanding missionary work in Brazil, considering that already had missionary work in São Paulo, Sorocaba and Jundiaí, led by missionaries: Alfredo Winderlich, Waldemar John Sjöberg, Olaf Berg and also the missionary Esther Danielsson. The first president of the Convention was the pastor Pedro Falcon. On this occasion is sent by the newly organized convention, the first missionary couple, Annie and Alcides Orrigo, to the city of Santa Rosa. In 1966, also in the city of Ijuí, the Convention had its name changed to: CONVENTION OF CHURCHES BAPTIST INDEPENDENT, which remains today.  With the organization of the Convention of Baptist Churches Independent in 1952, missionary fronts were opened in almost all states. In addition, work has expanded to Paraguay, Peru and Portugal.  From the Regional Convention 1988 are arranged. Through them are met the needs of each region. On November 11, 2017 was organized the Convention of Baptist Churches Independent in Bahia (CIBIBA), for the purpose of:  Create and execute mission projects; Create and maintain cultural, literary, educational and welfare institutions; Encourage fraternity between affiliated churches; Act as Advisor to the Board affiliated churches; Ensure the unit Independent Baptist.

Safety Watch is a product designed for children and parents. The app can be connected with the watch by wearing the watch on the children’s wrist and its supporting app on the parents’ mobile phone. Parents can make mutual calls between the watch and the mobile phone, accurately locate the children’s position, and send voice message between the app and the watch by setting watch-related functions in the app. Main Functional Features: 1.Phone Function: The phone module is installed in the hardware of the watch to allow calls between the phone and the watch, and between watches, thereby making communication and connection between parents and children more convenient.  2.Location Function: A GPS chip and WiFi module are installed in the hardware of the watch, enabling the APP to show the precise position of the watch whether outdoors or indoors. 3.Chat Function: Voice messages can be sent between the watch and the APP, realizing a new form of communication between children and parents.  4.Step Counting Function: The child’s number of steps can be viewed on the watch in order to help the parents record the child’s progress step by step and ensure their healthy growth. 5.Class Mode: Parents can set the times of the child’s classes. Hello folks! Welcome to Tech-Freedom for Visually Impaired. There is no doubt that over the last few years various apps were developed for the visually challenged to tackle various issues like screen reader, word processers, pdf readers and so on. In this scenario, we (V.I. Developers) are here with the multi-feature android app “Tech-Freedom”. Tech-Freedom is a multi-feature android app. It is ads free and cost-free app. It is stable from android 5 to 13. It has following features: 1.	App Backup. 2.	Audio Editor 3.	Cash Reader. 4.	Document Converter. 5.	Document Saver. 6.	Image Reader. 7.	Instant Reader. 8.	Link Saver. 9.	My Player. 10.	Notepad. 11.	Password Saver. 12.	PDF Reader. 13.	Text Translator. 14.	Video Editor 15.	Voice Recorder. These features are developed with having accessibility into the mind. Also, Accessibility is evaluated with Google’s accessibility suite (Talkback) during development. *App Backup: By using this feature, you’ll be able to take and share backup of your installed apps. Backed up apps will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/App Backups. *Audio Editor: Audio Editor is one of the most demanding features of our app. It’ll allow you to cut and merge audios. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Cash Reader: Blind people are often stuck while detecting currencies. To solve that problem, we design our own AI neural network to detect currencies using phone’s camera. Currently we’re only supporting Indian bank notes: 10 Rupee. 20 Rupee. 50 Rupee. 100 Rupee. 200 Rupee. 500 Rupee. 2000 Rupee. *Document Converter: This feature helps you to convert PDF, office and TXT files with each other. The converted files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Document Saver: By using Document Saver, you’ll be able to create TXT and PDF files from your text very easily. The saved files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Documents. *Image Reader: By using Tech-Freedom, your images will speak to you Directly. We have both online and offline image reader. Online image reader is most advance and accurate image processer. Whereas offline image reader is designed to be worked offline. *Instant Reader: An Instant Reader is used to instantly read out the text in front of camera. *Link Saver: By using our Link Saver, you’ll have all your important links saved. *My Player: My Player is used to play audios and videos on your device. *Notepad: By using our online notepad, you’ll be able to save your notes online. *Password Saver: By using our Password Saver, you’ll be able to save your account’s passwords offline. *PDF Reader: Reading PDF is more challenging task for a visually impaired. But it’ll be very easy to read it now with our most accurate and fast PDF Reader. It has many features to perform on your PDFs. Also, you can copy, translate, save, export and share content of your PDFs very easily. Ability to set bookmark is added too. You can also open your password protected PDFs very easily. In today’s world, PDF is not creating with just text, but it’s composed of scanned documents and images. With our advance and most accurate OCR engine, your PDFs can be rendered very well. *Text Translator: Text Translator is used to translate your text within 135 languages. *Video Editor: An accessible video editor is the dream of visually impaired. It includes: Video Cutter. Video Merger. Video to Audio. Image to Video. Output files will be stored inside Internal Storage/Tech-Freedom/Outputs. *Voice Recorder: By using Voice Recorder, you can record your audios. Official website of Tech-Freedom: https://techfreedom.in For any queries / suggestion, email us: info@techfreedom.in Best regards! V.I. Developers.

- View and download files in your Android, through PC, Mac, iPhone, Linux, Win Phone or other devices in the local area network - Use web browser without downloading additional software - Support folding screen - Support dark theme - Can directly open pictures, videos, logs - Simple operation, anyone can use - Via LAN, no data cable required - Through some browsers, you can even edit pictures, videos, etc. directly - You can set a login password to prevent your file from being viewed by others in the LAN - Well-designed UI - Serving static files in android  **Comparison with FTP:**  If used to view pictures, videos, logs, etc., the HTTP protocol is much more convenient than the FTP protocol. HTTP can open media and log files directly in the browser. With the help of some powerful functions of the browser, you can even mark pictures and videos directly. Because of security, more and more browsers are abandoning the FTP protocol.  The operation is much simpler than FTP, and you don't need to care about the messy and annoying FTP options such as various ports, parameters, and authorizations.  **For IT practitioners:**  If you are an IT practitioner, this is an excellent tool for transmitting screenshots, logs, and videos. You can open the screenshots directly in the browser and mark them, send to others.  Serving folder as webpage just like "python -m http.server" in computer.  **For ordinary users:**  Just took a photo or video with your cellphone and want to view or modify it on PC? It can be viewed and downloaded directly in the browser on the computer side.  If you want to share a file with another phone, but don't want to download all kinds of messy file transfer apps, open the browser to get the file you want to share.
